# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok king of kings , the #-year-old winner of one of europe 's top races , will stand at stud in the united states .
# ::alignments
(s / stand-01
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "King"
                  :op2 "of"
                  :op3 "Kingdom")
            :ARG0-of (w / win-01
                  :ARG1 (r / race-02
                        :quant 1
                        :ARG1-of (ii / include-91
                              :ARG2 (r2 / race-02
                                    :mod (t / top)
                                    :location (c / continent
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "Europe")))))
                  :age (t2 / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 1
                        :unit (y / year))))
      :ARG2 (s2 / stud)
      :location (c2 / country
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 "United"
                  :op2 "States")))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok un secretary-general ban ki-moon welcomed thursday the release of the ## remaining south korean hostages held by the taliban for over six weeks .
# ::alignments
(w / welcome-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Ban"
                  :op2 "Ki-moon")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :polarity -
                  :ARG2 (s / secretary
                        :mod (g / general))))
      :ARG1 (r / release-01
            :ARG1 (h2 / hostage
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "South"
                              :op2 "Korea"))
                  :ARG1-of (r2 / remain-01)
                  :ARG1-of (h3 / hold-01
                        :ARG0 (c2 / criminal-organization
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Taliban"))
                        :duration (o / over
                              :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                                    :quant 6
                                    :unit (w2 / week)))))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t2 / thursday))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok china announced wednesday limits for how much melamine its dairy products can contain , seeking to curb the use of the chemical which has killed four children and sickened ##,### .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (a2 / announce-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "china"))
            :ARG1 (l / limit-01
                  :ARG1 (m / massamine-00
                        :ARG1 (p2 / product
                              :mod (d / dairy)
                              :poss p)
                        :ARG1-of (c / contain-01
                              :ARG0 p2
                              :ARG1-of (p3 / possible-01)))
                  :time (d2 / date-entity
                        :weekday (w / wednesday))))
      :op2 (s / seek-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (c2 / curb-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (u / use-01
                        :ARG1 (c3 / chemical
                              :ARG0-of (k / kill-01
                                    :ARG1 (c4 / child
                                          :quant 4))
                              :ARG0-of (s2 / sicken-01))))))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok a special flight on friday took accused australian drug trafficker tony mokbel from greece back to his home country to face murder and narcotics charges .
# ::alignments
(t / take-01
      :ARG0 (f / fly-01
            :ARG1-of (s / special-02)
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (f2 / friday)))
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Tony"
                  :op2 "Mokbel")
            :source (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Greece"))
            :ARG1-of (a / accuse-01
                  :ARG2 (t2 / traffic-01
                        :ARG1 (d2 / drug))))
      :ARG3 (b / back)
      :destination (c2 / country
            :mod (h / home)
            :poss p)
      :purpose (f3 / face-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (c3 / charge-05
                        :ARG1 p
                        :ARG2 (m / murder-01
                              :ARG0 p))
                  :op2 (c4 / charge-05
                        :ARG1 p
                        :ARG2 (n3 / narcotic)))))

            :ARG1 (a / act-02
                  :mod (m2 / military))
            :ARG2 (o / option
                  :purpose (d2 / deal-01

                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Iran"))))))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (s2 / saturday))
      :time (a2 / after
            :op1 (d4 / discuss-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (ii2 / issue-02)
                  :ARG2 (p4 / person
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (c3 / country
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "U.S."))

                                    :mod (s3 / senior)))))))

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :polarity -
                  :location (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Iran")))
            :ARG2 (p / percentage-entity
                  :value "1/2")
            :ARG1-of (e2 / equal-01
                  :ARG2 (n2 / number
                        :quant-of (p2 / person
                              :mod c
                              :ARG0-of (h / have-03
                                    :polarity -
                                    :ARG1 (j / job))))))
      :ARG1 r2
      :time (t / today)
      :medium (l / language
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 "English"))
      :ARG1-of (l2 / local-02))

# ::id 9 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok royal bank of canada reported wednesday that its first quarter net income was up six percent , compared to the same period last year , at ### million dollars -lrb- about ### million us -rrb- .

            :mod (r2 / royal)
            :location (c / city
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Canada")))
      :ARG1 (u / up-02
            :ARG1 (ii / income
                  :mod (n2 / net)
                  :poss b
                  :time (q / quarter
                        :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                              :value 1)))
            :ARG2 (p / percentage-entity
                  :value 6)
            :ARG1-of (c2 / compare-01
                  :ARG2 ii
                  :mod n2
                  :time (p2 / period
                        :ARG1-of (s / same-01)
                        :time (y / year
                              :mod (l / last)))))
      :ARG3 (a / about
            :op1 (m / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 10000000
                  :unit (d / dollar)))
      :time (w / wednesday))

# ::id 12 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the curious case of the mysterious letter from zimbabwe 's opposition leader , morgan tsvangirai , to south africa 's president , thabo mbeki , got a new chapter this weekend that raised yet more questions about mbeki 's credibility as the regional mediator in zimbabwe 's increasingly tumultuous political crisis .

                                          :op1 "Zimbabwe"))

                  :ARG2 (p2 / person
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Thabo"
                              :op2 "Mbeki")
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (c3 / country
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "South"
                                          :op2 "Africa"))
                              :ARG2 (p3 / president)))
                  :mod (m / mystery))
            :ARG1-of (c4 / curious-01))
      :ARG1 (c5 / chapter
            :ARG1-of (n5 / new-01)
            :ARG0-of (r / raise-01
                  :ARG1 (q / question-01
                        :ARG1 (c6 / credibility
                              :poss p2
                              :mod (m2 / mediator
                                    :mod (r2 / region)
                                    :location (c7 / crisis
                                          :mod (p4 / politics)
                                          :mod (t / tumultuous

                        :ARG1-of (h2 / have-quant-91

            :time (w / weekend
                  :mod (t2 / this))))

                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Lankan")))
                  :ARG2 (m / minister
                        :mod (d / deputy))))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (h2 / have-03
                  :ARG0 (t / talk-01
                        :ARG1 (p2 / peace)
                        :ARG2 (t2 / tiger

                  :mod (s3 / succeed-01)
                  :quant (p3 / percentage-entity
                        :value 100)))
      :op2 (s4 / see-01
            :ARG1 (s5 / solve-01

                  :mod (p4 / politics)))

            :month 2))
